{"tid":597164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方接獲市民報案　稱南生圍發現疑似盛載機油膠筒","createTime":"2018-03-18T11:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T16:22:29.000Z","uid":37554,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfa8a75b41c0edd881d9e5bf0f4c37f34b31a7e","tid":597164,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1386494_1_L_20180318171424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1386494_1_L_20180318171424.jpg&h=60b1eb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇表示，昨日收到市民舉報，表示於南生圍發現一個載著疑似機油的塑膠筒，擔心與早前發生的火警有關。鄺俊宇指，該名市民已經報警，據悉警方已向他錄取口供。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆查詢時表示，已接獲市民報案，表示於南生圍發現載有液體的塑膠容器，警方已檢取證物作化驗。<br />\n<br />\n南生圍上星期接連發生火警，消防經初步調查，相信起火原因有可疑。警方將火列作縱火案處理，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"6feafed677185f436164933a804bf45f49c67ddd","tid":597164,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386494-20180318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386494-20180318.htm&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=12e0d716\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386494-20180318.htm&h=c65ce729\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386494-20180318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4364efa45766ba1d6cb3c2fe2144ff46d2bf062e","tid":597164,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2c7a78a2d1d5fb92777cafcde2ab43eab1ad64f","tid":597164,"uid":105538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"無可疑 close files"},{"pid":"e264069383d89019a572aa2f6a384e7666b50723","tid":597164,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆